## Usage Example
```python
from core.tools.log_integration_extended import SystemLogIntegration

# 생성
integration = SystemLogIntegration()

# 권한 부여
integration.grant_permissions(
    agent_id='my_agent',
    log_types=['syslog', 'daemon'],
    read_only=True,
    max_lines=500
)

# 시스템 로그 접근
result = integration.get_system_log_access(
    agent_id='my_agent',
    log_types=['syslog'],
    lines=100
)

# 에러 분석
errors = integration.analyze_system_errors(
    agent_id='my_agent',
    hours=1,
    severity='error'
)
```

